      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>State of Mind</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Sitting on a branch , Playing my guitar </l>
          <l>And time just barely just barely goes by </l>
          <l>Over me birds fly </l>
          <l>Awaken from the sound </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>I try (Try to get out of) </l>
          <l>This state of mind (To feel like I'm alive) </l>
          <l>Be here and now </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Resting in a field I tell myself again - "Do this more often" </l>
          <l>Time is slowing down </l>
          <l>feel like I can hold </l>
          <l>Hold it in my palm</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
